programme.desc: JT and Steve send Das Boat up to Austin to do a little urban angling. programme.title: Das Boat

programme.desc: Frank Smethurst and Mustache Rob circle back to some of their old favorite stomping grounds on the Savannah River in Augusta, Georgia. programme.title: Das Boat
programme.desc: Mustache Rob and Frank are back on the Savannah River in Georgia, headed 50+ miles downstream into water that they haven't seen before. programme.desc: Steve hauls Dos Boat to Boyne City, Michigan. Janis Putelis connects with trout fishing guide Brian Kozminski. programme.desc: Dos Boat crosses the Straits of Mackinaw and heads west to the Wisconsin, U.P. border. Joe Cermele teams up Tim Landwehr. They burn Tim‚ home river on a fishing show.
